          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "おすすめの資格"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-ylnfgv11i",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-n0qyycjm5",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "さらに、職場によっては、以下のような資格も給与アップに繋がる可能性があります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-mm9p15vzi",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-le9z221wy-9258c214-ef41-4eae-b4ac-dbe6820663e8",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-le9z221wy-cf8cc705-063d-4ae7-b0c5-d9c360c1c0f3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "喀痰吸引等研修"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-le9z221wy-c7c47252-cef1-401f-aca1-0752e5f0e38c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 医療行為である喀痰吸引や経管栄養の知識・技術を習得する研修です。修了することで、これらの業務を行うことが可能になり、資格手当が支給される場合があります。ただし、実施できる範囲は医療機関によって異なるため、事前に確認が必要です。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "medical-notice-282b44e8-057f-4e02-b9e4-f90fa342c441",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "medical-notice-span-5224b309-816c-464d-a7ac-7440ea4168c6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手は注射や点滴などの医療行為を担当できません。必要な処置がある場合は、できるだけ看護師に共有して指示を仰ぎましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-yecwi4d06",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-o42hfql6v-d3ab7635-0248-4e96-ac8a-7d5df22324fa",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-o42hfql6v-bb1b4a78-9fc7-43a9-aa90-26fd15e9b713",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "認知症ケア専門士"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-o42hfql6v-9143869b-fd3b-4494-ba43-9145ed647132",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 認知症ケアに関する専門的な知識と技術を証明する民間資格です。認知症患者が多い病院や施設では、資格手当が支給される可能性があります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-o6hjludqx",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-540kkyy6j-1c36d79e-af48-48bd-bdf0-38ba2bed956f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-540kkyy6j-cdbf5dd7-b45d-4709-86ba-5476fab0a888",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "MOS（マイクロソフト オフィス スペシャリスト）"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-540kkyy6j-4e56ae8e-a0bf-4d61-91fc-aa8186337470",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 看護助手は、事務作業を行うこともあります。MOS資格を取得することで、PCスキルを証明でき、業務効率化に貢献できることをアピールできます。直接的な資格手当がなくても、昇給や転職時に有利になる可能性があります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-bamshjhgu",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-lpi4ovgxt",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "参考: 厚生労働省 令和5年度介護従事者処遇状況等調査"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-vgjbhkjtm",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-24i0fp41p",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "2. 給与水準の高い職場へ転職する"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-5rfb6yq1v",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-yk6yu50fm",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "給与が高い傾向にある職場"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-sjeib3wr8",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-gz3e5o56m",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "加えて、以下の点も考慮すると良いでしょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-6u33m2tss",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-w1033zem6-bf085711-02e2-4360-ba0c-d96c00fd2788",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-w1033zem6-36bdad6f-56cb-4fdd-9939-3f8e79cedf71",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "診療科"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-w1033zem6-b4810e5f-ccd4-4e7c-bae7-cd2290cf5503",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 例えば、救命救急センターや集中治療室（ICU）など、専門性の高い診療科を持つ病院では、看護助手にも専門的な知識やスキルが求められるため、給与水準が高い傾向があります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-lfawhs350",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-jelxysxuv-7b514496-6f29-47c5-8db0-641543dbbf73",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-jelxysxuv-33853316-0eb9-4e00-b5c6-b451fb3fbd2c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "福利厚生"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-jelxysxuv-8eeed65b-d750-430a-8702-897a17cec58f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 給与だけでなく、住宅手当、家族手当、託児所利用補助など、福利厚生が充実している職場を選ぶことも、実質的な収入アップに繋がります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-c60mbqc7z",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-f2ebnlu6b",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "転職活動のポイント"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-9ya2t9i7c",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-3bgxkgvh3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "転職活動を行う際には、以下の準備をしておきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-hz4c5fe4u",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-c2j3m3hy2-463af690-324d-4f1a-b683-25f3d2dd065d",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-c2j3m3hy2-fddc5930-31d7-49de-baa5-3c8855ebb662",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "自己分析"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-c2j3m3hy2-25552bbd-ac60-4e4e-b72a-351866db234e",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 自分のスキル、経験、強み、弱みを整理し、どのような職場で活躍できるのかを明確にしましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-i86zpmh3j",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-8yvbj5udb-641d5394-4480-4064-8664-52c9c6d5e947",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-8yvbj5udb-b4a421fd-705a-4851-91e3-5eef23e07c5c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "希望条件の明確化"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-8yvbj5udb-c94d1c05-63cf-48d8-b960-473434ff84a0",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 給与、勤務時間、勤務地、福利厚生など、希望する条件を具体的に書き出しましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-wrc9jkded",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-vnemy12bx-1fd98ecf-38fd-48e8-91fc-694e9c9eac1a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-vnemy12bx-f14fab04-aebf-421e-a273-c4863792acfe",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "情報収集"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-vnemy12bx-2fec1c2a-3041-4db1-8462-e32268cc95b3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 病院のホームページや口コミサイトなどで、給与水準や職場の雰囲気を調べましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-q7mdvge8z",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-rbtli6p30",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "3. 役職者（リーダー）を目指す"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-2uh3vifyp",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-b69lxa9z3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "役職者になるためのポイント"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h3"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-1bvxcg2jw",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-2s9l4lpxx",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "役職者を目指す上で、日々の業務の中で意識したいことは以下の通りです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-7i8u29dfg",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pfcnpjxi8-5f6d7c9b-f429-4b67-99ed-5e4acbcf50de",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pfcnpjxi8-74494e61-4912-48ef-a55f-6db8a109c4fb",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "責任感を持つ"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pfcnpjxi8-0e40cd76-a8be-4272-b6a0-f8b3f11ac93a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 自分の役割を理解し、責任を持って業務を遂行しましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-v1sosdt1y",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pu7iac0t0-579da831-f320-4f14-82fd-2efdb9e52e31",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pu7iac0t0-74134be7-61a4-42b4-9bb7-396f82073284",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "向上心を持つ"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-pu7iac0t0-115715c9-e3a1-4ca0-a276-93007d08382f",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": 常に新しい知識やスキルを学び、自己研鑽に励みましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-ivjz3ylhk",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-m5ksrybe7-2ac97091-0d89-48c2-b204-4968b190b4fe",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "*   "
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-m5ksrybe7-37464b39-80b3-4cc1-a961-0f62600f7221",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "strong"
          ],
          "text": "チームワークを大切にする"
        },
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-m5ksrybe7-48535464-5519-4ff8-8375-ba4dcd282d27",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": ": チームの一員として、他のスタッフと協力し、より良い医療を提供できるように努めましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-045chh32n",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-ixgc5jroe",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "これらの点を意識して日々の業務に取り組むことで、周囲からの信頼を得ることができ、役職者への道が開ける可能性が高まります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block-1760819037764-vhbsgq6mx",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-1760819037764-6pm0kx5qf",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "今回の記事が、看護助手として働く皆様のキャリアアップの一助となれば幸いです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "internal-link-14510ace-1a3c-421b-907c-558170f295cb",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "internal-link-span-intro-9d46738b-61e0-4085-9135-525ea553a0f5",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "詳しくは"
        },
        {
          "_key": "internal-link-span-title-1e433180-6e7d-4ecf-95e9-9d9a726c17da",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "link-5b68fef6-2d2b-48e5-85c9-7d01a2b54370"
          ],
          "text": "「看護助手から看護師へ転職したら年収はどれくらい増える？」"
        },
        {
          "_key": "internal-link-span-outro-a42acb2a-2c3c-47be-80b2-2183838d2afd",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "でも現場のポイントを詳しく解説しています。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-5b68fef6-2d2b-48e5-85c9-7d01a2b54370",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "/posts/nursing-assistant-salary-increase-nurse"
        }
      ],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "block--8446521892015027344",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "span-373389077394698207",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "まとめ"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-37e44bbb-b4c4-489d-81ab-7e3f7830e81e",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-22f8f84c-ec69-42b0-bcd3-c3e438cf2269",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "看護助手の年収を上げるための方法3選でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-7c648bcf-2b62-43f2-9439-8f0b7531b62c",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-51bfdc3a-1435-4ee7-a956-df2459173d2c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-7bf1b7c9-8df0-45e8-8786-8f46972269cf",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-4b9ef3e0-c731-4b99-807b-b820cd896546",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "1. 資格を取得して「資格手当」を狙うの視点でおすすめの資格に目を向ける"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-34666874-f10b-4d1c-9bb5-f2eaf636c80d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-9517cf5f-32bc-4bea-a188-b19e5bb77369",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "介護福祉士: 介護分野唯一の国家資格。取得することで、月5,000円〜15,000円程度の資格手当が支給されることが多…"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-e536497b-8cc1-46a1-93fe-c7a6a8e20c4a",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-d91dd0fb-2507-4eea-93a2-941bf628f2bc",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "あわてず一歩ずつ、チームと情報を共有しながら進めれば大丈夫です。今日の学びを小さく実践し、次の勤務につなげていきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
